akka.event.slf4j

Class Slf4jLoggingFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.event.slf4j.Slf4jLoggingFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LoggingFilter

    public class Slf4jLoggingFilter
extends java.lang.Object
implements LoggingFilter
    LoggingFilter that uses the log level defined in the SLF4J backend configuration (e.g. logback.xml) to filter log events before publishing the log events to the eventStream.
